description:
Hardwell presents Revealed Vol. 6 â†’ http://hwl.dj/REVRVol6
Hardwell - United We Are (Album) â†’ http://bit.ly/UNITEDWEARE

Calvin Harris feat. Ellie Goulding - Outside (Hardwell Remix)
After a year that saw him retain his crown of World #1 DJ for a second consecutive year, sweep in to dominate the festival landscape with colossal peak time performances everywhere from Future Music Festival in Australia to Tomorrowland's 10th anniversary edition in Belgium, as well as releasing his chart-dominating debut artist album United We Are, Hardwell also found the time to construct yet another dancefloor thriller, this time with his remix of Calvin Harris's satiable hit 'Outside'.

Stomping arpeggios followed by spacious break-downs that allows for British starlet Ellie Goulding's soaring falsetto to take centre stage, Hardwell steers Calvin's pop gem into a direction of pure unadulterated dance, complete with big-room drops and  an infectiously heavy beat.

Receiving its live premiere at his #UnitedWeAre kick-off shows that sold-out Amsterdam's  colossal Ziggo Dome, demonstrating Hardwell's true ability as a highly-respected artist both on the live circuit and within the studio, this unique edit of 'Outside' has already been causing a stir across social media and throughout online forums over the weekend, rousing up excitement for its impending release after thousands tuned in to hear the official mastered version in the latest episode of Hardwell On Air.  

Hardwell's remix of 'Outside' is out now on Calvin Harris's Fly Eye Records exclusive to Beatport and will be available via iTunes March 16th.
